<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Return Request Update - Bamboo Shop</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f9fc; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h2 { color: #2b7a0b; }
    .status-banner { 
      background: #e8f5e9; 
      border-left: 5px solid #2b7a0b; 
      padding: 15px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .status-text { font-weight: bold; color: #2b7a0b; text-transform: uppercase; }
    a.button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background: #2b7a0b; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
    a.button:hover { background: #25660a; }
    p { margin: 10px 0; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>The status of your return request for <strong>Order #{{returnId}}</strong> has been updated.</p>

    <div class="status-banner">
      Current Status: <span class="status-text">{{status}}</span>
    </div>

    {{#if (eq status "APPROVED")}}
    <p>Great news! Your return has been <strong>approved</strong>. Please follow the instructions in your dashboard to ship the items back to us.</p>
    {{else if (eq status "REJECTED")}}
    <p>Your return request has been <strong>declined</strong>. If you believe this is a mistake, please reply to this email or contact our support team.</p>
    {{else}}
    <p>Your return request is currently being processed. Status: <strong>{{status}}</strong>.</p>
    {{/if}}

    <a href="{{appUrl}}/profile/returns" class="button">View My Returns</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for shopping with Bamboo Shop!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br/>Bamboo Shop Team</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Bamboo Shop. This is an automated notification.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>